headline: Quantum Computing Inc. Positions Itself Between Quantum Hardware and Enterprise Adoption as Anson Funds Exits
summary: Quantum Computing Inc. develops software designed to connect emerging quantum processors with real-world enterprise applications. After Anson Funds exited its position, the focus now shifts to whether this middleware approach can translate early experimentation into durable commercial adoption.
